                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7171" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1786</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8149 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“小人物”如何推动大变革——迈皋桥社区医院的个性化医疗变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How &quot;Small Potato&quot; Promotes Big Changes--Road of Personalized Medical Reform in Maigaoqiao Primary Hospital</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张文红，赖秀萍，赵亚普，陈斯蕾，党蓓蕾</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">迈皋桥社区医院</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">专业组织；制度变革；(半)专业人士；知识生态；跨职业协作</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> professional organization, institutional change, (semi-)professionals, regime of knowledge, cross-professional collaboration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新技术快速应用、社会环境以及政策制度的变化，要求专业组织进行快速和深刻的变革。然而，当变革冲击到核心专业实践时，受益于既定制度安排的主导专业人士往往不愿意改变，组织该如何推进变革？案例描述了迈皋桥社区医院为响应宏观制度变迁而推进慢病管理的变革过程。该院的管理者发现变革不仅对护士的冲击更小，还有利于发挥其专长，提升其地位，从而在变革中扮演重要角色。管理者首先创造“自由试验区”提升护士对变革的信心和能力，然后建立不同科室和职业的“自由贸易区”缓和医护冲突，并通过护士的“连接”与“引流”形成“收益共享区”，实现医护携手推动变革。迈皋桥社区医院利用半专业人士推进变革的实践对于其它组织也有重要借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Recently, the rapid adoptions of new technologies, changes in the social environment, policies and systems have required professional organizations to reform professional practices rapidly and profoundly. However, when changes impact the core figures of professional practices, how can organizations move forward with change when dominant professionals who benefit from established institutional arrangements are often reluctant to change? This case describes the transformation process of Maigaoqiao Primary Hospital to promote personalized management of chronic disease in response to macro-institutional changes. In this process, the hospital&#39;s managers found that nurses not only faced lower impact of change, but also benefited from their expertise and elevated status, thus playing an important role in the change. The head first created a &quot;free experimental zone&quot; to enhance nurses&#39; confidence and ability to change, and then set up a &quot;free trade zone&quot; with different departments and occupations to ease the conflict between physicians and nurses, and further exert the &quot;connection&quot; and &quot;redirecting&quot; role of nurses to form a &quot;profit sharing zone&quot;, which realizes new institutional changes by promoting both physicians and nurses to work together. The practice of using semi-professionals to drive change in this case has implications for other organizations as well.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宏观制度变迁引发组织制度变革；外部环境变化下的组织战略选择过程；战略转型中的商业模式制定；(半)专业人士、知识生态与专业组织中的制度变革策略；地位理论与跨职业协作</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
